description:
Animal's Super Senses - Episode 10: The Night | Wildlife Documentary

Watch 'Animal's Super Senses - Episode 11' here: https://youtu.be/cITs4EaES9c

In this episode of Animal Super Senses, we find out more about the animals that live in the shadows and the adaptations they need to survive
Nocturnal animals have taken to this dark world for good reason: they escape predators, avoid the heat of the day, and  take their turn sharing food and resources in their niche. But to navigate life in the dark, you need some special abilities to cope with the lack of light.
